data.description: This move in ready one-story home has an open floor plan, 9-foot ceilings, 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, 2 ceiling fans in living room, kitchen has recess lights and large costume cabinets with a eat-in breakfast bar, laminate flooring, carpet, linoleum. The interior of home has fresh paint through-out the home. Easy access to Loop 1604, Loop 410 and highway 90.
